Mary Szela works as Chief Executive Officer at Melinta Therapeutics. She serves as its President and served as its Chairperson since January 2013. Ms. Szela has been Senior Vice President of Global Strategic Marketing and Services at Abbott Diabetes Care, Inc. since January 2010. Ms. Szela served as a Senior Vice President of Global Strategic Marketing and Services Pharmaceutical Products Group at Abbott Laboratories since 2010 and also served as its Senior Vice President of U S Pharmaceuticals from 2008 to 2009. Ms. Szela served more than two decades in senior roles at Abbott Laboratories. Ms. Szela served as Senior Vice President, U.S. Pharmaceuticals. at Abbott Diabetes Care, Inc. She served as Senior Vice President of Pharmaceutical Operations of Abbott’s commercial pharmaceutical business in the United States from August 2007 to 2008. She served as Corporate Officer at Abbott Laboratories since 2001. She served as Vice President of Commercial Pharmaceutical Operations at Abbott Laboratories since 2006, where she was responsible for sales and marketing of many of Abbott’s pharmaceutical brands, including HUMIRA. Ms. Szela served as Vice President of Pharmaceutical Products, Primary Care Operations of Abbott Laboratories from 2001 to 2006. Ms. Szela joined Abbott in 1987 and has held several leadership positions at Abbott, including Divisional Vice President of Hospital Products Business Sector from 1998 to 2001. She served as General Manager of Anesthesia, Hospital Products since 1998. Ms. Szela worked for the University of Illinois Hospital. She served as the Chairperson of Rib-X Pharmaceuticals, Inc. since January 2013 and has been its Director since January 2013. She has been a Director of Coherus Biosciences Inc. since July 2014 and Novo Nordisk A/S since March 19, 2015. She has been a Director of Arisaph Pharmaceuticals, Inc. since 2007 and Receptos, Inc. since July 2014. She has been a Director of Melinta Therapeutics, Inc. since January 2013. She serves as a Director of Suneva Medical, Inc.



